trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A tracking service that implements the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification> interface raises a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event to notify the runtime tracking infrastructure that new instances of a particular workflow <xref:System.Type> should no longer be tracked.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]En spårningstjänst som implementerar det <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>gränssnitt aktiverar en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>händelse att Avisera körtiden spårning infrastruktur för de nya instanserna av ett visst arbetsflöde <xref:System.Type>inte längre att spåras.</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>

trans-unit.source: The tracking service uses a ProfileRemovedEventArgs to provide the workflow <xref:System.Type> to the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Spårningstjänsten använder en ProfileRemovedEventArgs för att tillhandahålla arbetsflödet <xref:System.Type>körningstillstånd spårning infrastruktur.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> uses a ProfileRemovedEventArgs when it raises the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileRemoved?displayProperty=fullName> event.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>använder en ProfileRemovedEventArgs när den genererar den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileRemoved?displayProperty=fullName>händelse.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileRemoved?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>

trans-unit.source: After a tracking service raises the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event, the runtime tracking infrastructure will no longer associate a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> with the specified workflow <xref:System.Type> for that tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Efter en spårningstjänst genererar den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>händelse spårning körningsinfrastrukturen associeras inte längre en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>med angivet arbetsflöde <xref:System.Type>för av Spårningstjänsten.</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: If you use this constructor when you raise a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved> event inside a tracking service, you must explicitly set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Om du använder den här konstruktorn när du höjer en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>händelsen inuti en spårningstjänst måste anges explicit <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileRemoved>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs"></xref> class that applies to the specified workflow <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs"> </xref> klass som gäller för den angivna arbetsflöden <xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A new instance of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs> is created with <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> set to the specified <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: En ny instans av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs>skapas med <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>inställd på den angivna <xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The workflow <xref:System.Type> for which the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> should be removed.
Gets or sets the workflow <xref:System.Type> for which the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> should be removed.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger arbetsflödet <xref:System.Type>som den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"> </xref> bör tas bort.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: WorkflowType specifies the workflow <xref:System.Type> for which a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> no longer exists, and which, therefore, should no longer be tracked by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: WorkflowType anger arbetsflödet <xref:System.Type>som en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>finns inte längre och som därför bör inte längre att spåras av körningen spårning infrastruktur.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Type>
